race.description: Ole Kirk First Yearlings C,G&E Handicap (Bm72)
race.comment: MISSILE SEEKER (3) comes here in peak condition and will relish the strong tempo. Worked home well from back in the field with a fast finishing third over 1400m at this track. Look for him launching late. DUVANA (2) big jump in class at his second run back and left a little flat footed in the straight when sixth over 1400m at Randwick. Strips fitter and expect to see him a little closer with the 3kg claim. Worthy contender in this class. DEPUTIZE (7) returned from a lengthy break with the big weight when he wound up strongly from last on the turn to finish third over 1200m at Gosford. Looks set for a good prep. ANTHRACITE (4) is a promising gelding making his stable debut for the Pride camp, after impressing in his debut prep in SA. Readied with two trials and should be savaging the line.
